'''Anise''' (commonly called '''aniseed''') is a medical herb that grows white flowers annually. It is planted in early spring, as soon as the ground warms up, then it should grow to about 18 inches. The '''anise '''seeds are used to make many treatments including cough treatment, epilepsy treatment, sedative, antiseptic and more.

